    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited for whoever ends up with this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, kept it spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a scratch on it! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
