    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including Dr. VANOS solenoid upgrades, ACL rod bearing replacement, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains factory-spec rigidity with zero bushing deflection, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque vectoring. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no swirl marks or rock chips. A true purist\u2019s specimen with a documented service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
