    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless original paint and deep luster with no chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state, featuring supple leather seating with no signs of wear, original factory floor mats, and that unmistakable new-car scent. Every service milestone has been documented at the authorized dealership, ensuring the mechanical integrity is as perfect as its aesthetic. With exceptionally low mileage and a completely clean history, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
