    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute gem! I\u2019m parting with my pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in truly stunning, showroom condition. It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept tucked away in a garage, and looks like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection! It drives like a total dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the dealership stress, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
