    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering high-revving performance through six individual throttle bodies and a bespoke tuned exhaust manifold. The double-VANOS system has been fully overhauled for precise cam phasing, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec torsional rigidity. The suspension retains original geometry with updated dampers, ensuring telepathic turn-in. This is a mechanically synchronized, concours-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
